/*
  * ============================================================
  *  EMRC-IDS — Integrated IDS with ILI9341 TFT Display
 *  Hardware : ESP32 DevKit V1 38-pin
 *  Modules  : MCP2515 + NRF24 + CC1101 + ILI9341 TFT
 *
 *  LIBRARIES NEEDED (install via Library Manager):
 *  → MCP_CAN              by coryjfowler
 *  → RF24                 by TMRh20
 *  → ELECHOUSE_CC1101_SRC_DRV by LSatan
 *  → Adafruit ILI9341     by Adafruit
 *  → Adafruit GFX Library by Adafruit
 *
 *  PIN CONNECTIONS:
 *  ─────────────────────────────────────────
 *  SHARED SPI:
 *  MOSI → GPIO 23
 *  MISO → GPIO 19
 *  SCK  → GPIO 18
 *
 *  MCP2515:          NRF24 (adapter):
 *  CS   → GPIO 5     VCC  → 5V
 *  INT  → GPIO 35    CE   → GPIO 4
 *                    CSN  → GPIO 17
 *  CC1101:
 *  CS   → GPIO 16
 *
 *  ILI9341 TFT:
 *  VCC  → 3.3V
 *  GND  → GND
 *  CS   → GPIO 15
 *  DC   → GPIO 2
 *  RST  → GPIO 27
 *  SDI  → GPIO 23  (MOSI shared)
 *  SCK  → GPIO 18  (SCK shared)
 *  LED  → 3.3V
 *  SDO  → GPIO 19  (MISO shared)
 * ============================================================
 */

